_sText:
ze_Eerie_Escape_B1

  • Zombie Escape Map with only 1 Level with lasers at the end.
  • Humans have to survive for few minutes and then they will be teleported to the final hold of the map where they will have to survive lasers too.
  • 3 Different Secret spots (2 for humans and 1 more zombie).
  • 1 Special item for humans.
Map may contain bugs. Althrough I did my best to make it as furnished as possible, if you find any just let me know.

**You are not allowed to decompile this map and modify it**

However feel free to port it to CS:GO.

I will add more stages and update the map if given positive feedback.
